<a name="run"><b>run</b></a>
<pre>
  public void run()
</pre>
<dl>
  <dd> The run method is called when the thread is created.  It waits
(on a semaphor) for requests and notifications to arrive, and calls
the appropriate handle() method to process them.
</dl>
